{"tid":813221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5歲女童下體流血疑遭性侵　父親訴苦：兇手是玩具","createTime":"2018-09-10T09:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T00:05:50.000Z","uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"793d64ebc070147d1880e9b2ef0c441d9e2f9c2f","tid":813221,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:36:19.000Z","msg":"記者於慶璇／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n又發生狼父性侵女兒案件？林口長庚醫院本月3日一名5歲女童被送到急診室，醫生幫女童治療後，開立驗傷單，上頭寫著「疑似性侵」，同時通知社會局安置女童，讓年僅5歲女童下體受傷流血的人到底是誰？女童爸爸第一時間上網訴苦，說兇手是一根「玩具屋支架」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/10/1536426-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F1536426-XXL.jpg&h=7ec180c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲父親指女童從書桌跳下時，撞到「玩具屋支架」，導致下體流血。（圖／爆料公社）<br />\n<br />\n這名女童的爸爸在臉書《爆料公社》PO出醫院開立「疑遭性侵」的驗傷單，急得上網求救，說自己 「要暈倒了」，隨文還附上女兒檢傷證明，陰道出血、陰部有新撕裂傷。到底怎麼回事？根據該名爸爸PO文線索，2日發現女童在自己房間大哭，過去查看發生什麼事，就看見女兒下體流血，將女兒帶到長庚醫院急救，沒想到醫生竟然懷疑女兒「被性侵」！<br />\n<br />\n女童的爸爸還表示，女兒入院後，自己隔天忘記可以探望小孩，後來想起來要看孩子，小孩就被社工帶走，爸爸還用了「不知去向」來形容，「可以請各位幫忙嗎？我很著急找小孩，也聯絡不到這個社工，誰有認識這個社工可以幫忙找他手機？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/10/1536430-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F1536430-XXL.jpg&h=4c6afca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲驗傷單顯示，女童下體有新撕裂傷，疑遭性侵。（圖／爆料公社）<br />\n<br />\n但貼文一出，好多網友開始打臉，說這樣的傷勢怎麼可能是女童自己造成，當爸爸怎麼會忘了到醫院探望小孩，又在留言底下回應「是的剛好命中。滑進去」，現在PO文只讓人認為此地無銀三百兩。而《三立新聞網》試圖聯繫PO文的女童爸爸，至截稿前尚未回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/10/1536465-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F1536465-XXL.jpg&h=c9e638a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲面對網友種種質疑，爸爸回應「是的剛好命中。滑進去」（圖／爆料公社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=427764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D427764&d=UqtrghsjQ4wKef0B79lzCcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=9c631746\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D427764&h=6cc41a58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=427764</a>"},{"pid":"5d1d9a97d0b58255dd29893cf36a3f63f2ac831b","tid":813221,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9585051f0e6507b97c70562440886880b9f58178","tid":813221,"uid":36187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:40:41.000Z","msg":"5歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f5a5b5b2712380e4d90d2aeaecfa4280d89ff9","tid":813221,"uid":78347,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"奇蹟之插入"},{"pid":"d9ebe661f21932077f994036689e21a2c2e457a1","tid":813221,"uid":68219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"屌你咁撚大支支架你屎眼都塞唔入啦"},{"pid":"5b941ed490deffa24aca650ccc724f6f0d4bd177","tid":813221,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:46:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會咁岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba510b74f554257e7be57b9c14b413dbd0f249a0","tid":813221,"uid":65984,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"個細路5歲, 係意外定比老豆搞實問得出, 唔好跟車太貼"},{"pid":"5757030747c36725646e2efee8de28f467ce76e4","tid":813221,"uid":151877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"新北+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99c16e10b483b868e337109129ca3b61da0dc3a","tid":813221,"uid":36390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:03:41.000Z","msg":"重判<img src=\"/assets/fac